<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ جُرَيْجٍ:</span> قَالَ طَاوُسٌ، <span class="c1">" تُرَحَّلُ الرِّحَالُ إِلَى مَسْجِدَيْنِ: مَسْجِدِ مَكَّةَ، وَمَسْجِدِ الْمَدِينَةِ "</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>